# ========================================
# COMMENTS AND NOTES
# ========================================

# This .forceignore file is designed for Salesforce DX deployments
# It excludes common development artifacts, sensitive data, and unnecessary files
# while preserving essential Salesforce metadata for deployment

# To include a specific file that's being ignored, use:
# !force-app/main/default/path/to/file

# To include a specific directory that's being ignored, use:
# !force-app/main/default/path/to/directory/

# Remember: .forceignore affects deployment, .gitignore affects version control
# Both should be configured appropriately for your project needs
**/jsconfig.json

**/.eslintrc.json

